00:34:43.786 --> 00:34:55.131
I can feel it. It's like you're pushing for that fresh water over those people.

00:34:55.132 --> 00:35:13.519
I can feel it as you're pushing against that, saying no to King Charles and that demonic influence holding back the religion, holding back like a stronghold trying to keep the Gospel out from their ears.

00:35:13.520 --> 00:35:31.088
But when I'm pushing, it's like pushing through mud. Does that make sense to you all?

00:35:31.089 --> 00:35:59.866
We call forth the living water today for the young Davids to rise up in England and it goes clear into Ireland.

00:35:59.867 --> 00:37:04.796
I'm seeing Ireland right now. Nothing is too far gone. I hear the Spirit of the Lord say, 'It goes clear into France.

00:37:04.798 --> 00:38:24.509
This tentacle goes clear into France. Now it goes into Germany.'I'm praying over the new Prime Minister of Canada.

00:38:24.510 --> 00:40:02.239
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say, 'If you're praying for England, you're sowing seeds for your country.

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:14.095
You're sowing seeds of revival. When you're believing for somebody else's need, you're sowing seeds for your need.

00:40:14.096 --> 00:40:19.643
As you pray in the spirit for yours, you might say, "Well, this doesn't have anything to do with me.

00:40:19.644 --> 00:40:26.127
I live in Poland. That doesn't have anything to do with me."No.

00:40:26.128 --> 00:40:35.029
You're sowing seeds by faith into what you're praying for and you'll reap a harvest for your country as you sow into it.

00:40:35.030 --> 00:40:37.879
Do you understand? I'm hearing this by the Spirit of the Lord.

00:40:37.880 --> 00:40:56.021
So, you're praying for Canada, Australia, and England, but not only are you helping them, you're reaping back fruit for America, China, Asia, and all over Africa.

00:40:56.022 --> 00:41:07.843
You're praying and believing, and as you help lift a brother out, you're sowing for yourself because God sees it.

00:41:07.844 --> 00:41:17.293
It's coming up out of your spirit. God hears it all; He knows it, and it all comes out.

00:41:17.294 --> 00:41:28.363
Do not say, "Well, this is a waste."No, you're believing for your brother and sister, and you're sowing on behalf of them.

00:41:28.364 --> 00:41:38.891
That's what you're doing right now. We're turning this in the spirit realm because it starts going like tentacles, and we don't give up.

00:41:38.892 --> 00:41:50.245
We say, "We're believing for revival all over the world."It's because people have not had a backbone to stand for the Word.

00:41:50.246 --> 00:42:03.991
Preachers have lost their salt. When you lose your salt, people don't get thirsty because salt causes us to draw for the living water.

00:42:03.992 --> 00:42:14.904
And if that living water is not being dished out because you lost your saltiness, that's what happens.

00:42:14.905 --> 00:42:26.583
Then this demonic blanket tries to come in over these nations to suffocate the Gospel. I see it when I'm going into it.

00:42:26.584 --> 00:42:34.662
I saw those English houses with the straw roofs and the old Tudor style homes with ivy growing.

00:42:34.663 --> 00:42:46.305
It was all trying to grow up around them and suffocate the life out of these houses. It was like the Dark Ages. They're trying to bury it.

00:42:46.306 --> 00:42:51.224
When you have shrubbery and things grow up around a house, it means nobody is taking care of it.

00:42:51.225 --> 00:42:57.866
You're losing ground because it's being buried. Christianity is trying to be buried by foliage.

00:42:57.867 --> 00:43:13.646
The Dark Ages are trying to come back over England. Maybe there's a lot more to this—why there's green and shrubbery all around these houses.

00:43:13.647 --> 00:43:19.679
I know that means life, but at the same time, it means there's no maintenance.

00:43:19.680 --> 00:43:36.040
Somebody needs to prune it back and make it look nice because it's not being maintained by the body of Christ.

00:43:36.041 --> 00:43:53.480
No, we're going to have revival. There needs to be more prayer.

00:43:53.481 --> 00:44:07.598
All's not lost. There's a new wave coming. I hear the sound of an abundance of rain coming.

00:44:07.599 --> 00:44:14.215
The enemy thought he won, but I'm going to bring one more wave that's coming.

00:44:14.216 --> 00:44:38.277
It will go from sea to shining sea. All throughout Europe, you will see the glory of the Lord rise upon you.

00:44:38.278 --> 00:45:02.218
The glory of the Lord is risen on you. Arise and shine, for the light has come, and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:45:02.219 --> 00:45:20.399
And now I see upon a wall a spout of water shooting out of this wall.

00:45:20.400 --> 00:45:58.078
It's the clearest looking water coming out of this wall, from the very foundation of the Word.

00:45:58.079 --> 00:46:10.378
All throughout Europe, all throughout the land. It's not a coincidence.

00:46:10.379 --> 00:46:42.885
You see the great shaking that will bring you to your knees. Pope Francis went home on Easter; this was a sign.

00:46:42.886 --> 00:46:56.515
I see Notre-Dame in France. I see the bells ringing in France.

00:46:56.516 --> 00:51:52.660
They are ringing all throughout the land. I see great revival spreading throughout Africa.

00:51:52.661 --> 00:52:16.629
As far as the eye can see, the greatest harvest you will see. All over Africa, you will see a great revival.

00:52:16.630 --> 00:52:34.144
I see witch doctors and satanic practices; I see them burning their witchcraft and their satanic rituals in barrels.

00:52:34.145 --> 00:52:40.566
They're giving their hearts to Jesus. I see them burning witchcraft.

00:52:40.568 --> 00:53:29.689
Witch doctors are getting afraid. Coming from the earth, I see gold deposits.

00:53:29.690 --> 00:53:54.955
I see gold and jewels coming out of the ground. I see gold. I see gold and emeralds.

00:53:54.956 --> 00:54:23.039
The emeralds are on top of the gold—green stones upon the gold. I see old mesquite trees and sandy soil.

00:54:23.040 --> 00:54:45.907
There are believers who are believing for this wealth transfer.

00:54:45.908 --> 00:54:54.622
They are asking the Lord for the wealth transfer, and I see the Lord is leading them to the gold deposits and emeralds.

00:54:54.623 --> 00:55:13.099
I see gold. Do they even have gold and emeralds in Africa? I see emeralds the size of your fist—huge, massive stones that have never been seen before.

00:55:13.100 --> 00:55:26.078
Gold nuggets and gold deposits are being found in the land, with emeralds the size of baseballs.

00:55:26.079 --> 00:55:59.614
Massive, purest emeralds. I see a lot of corruption around this.

00:55:59.615 --> 00:56:10.064
These people are like pirates—evil men who have taken this wealth from the people, keeping money from them.

00:56:10.065 --> 00:56:18.646
There is so much poverty. In this poverty, there are African cartels, like the drug cartels from Mexico.

00:56:18.647 --> 00:56:41.444
They have hidden the wealth. But I see this ground owned by ministers who are secretly digging and finding these deposits.

00:56:41.445 --> 00:56:52.850
They are dealing with this discreetly so they don't tell the cartels; they don't want to let on that they have this.

00:56:52.851 --> 00:57:07.838
But it is God's provision in the time of drought and famine in Africa for these ministers. Don't give up.

00:57:07.839 --> 00:57:38.879
In your time of fasting, praying, and seeking Me, He is showing you the secret things of the earth. It will come as a river.

00:57:38.880 --> 00:58:00.311
I even see water in places of great drought coming from the earth—water of provision, real drinking water coming forth out of springs.

00:58:00.312 --> 00:58:08.024
Supernatural water reserves are coming up out of the earth for you where you say, 'Well, there's no water here.

00:58:08.025 --> 00:58:17.998
How can we base a church out of here?'The water is there, and where the water is, the people will come.

00:58:17.999 --> 00:58:27.973
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say He is bringing you water out of the earth, and there will be revival around this water.

00:58:27.974 --> 00:58:43.256
A natural water He will provide to bring the living water to your tribe. Do you hear what I say to you by the Spirit of the Lord today?

00:58:43.257 --> 00:58:54.128
A supernatural water is coming for great things out of the depths of the earth.

00:58:54.129 --> 00:59:15.873
We call forth the water, for this will bring forth a living water where you'll never thirst again. Where there is water, there is life.

00:59:15.874 --> 00:59:30.917
There will be water coming forth out of natural springs in these dry places, and it will be an oasis. The body of Christ will be on it, and the people will come.

00:59:30.918 --> 00:59:47.139
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say, 'Oh Father, we call that water out of the ground.'Wells of living water!

00:59:47.140 --> 01:00:15.679
Great revival in Africa! Emeralds and gold will be the supply for food and water. You will bring it in.

01:00:15.680 --> 01:00:24.798
He is going to give you favor on who to do business with to cash in the gold and emeralds so that you are not caught off guard or hurt by people.

01:00:24.799 --> 01:00:40.589
You must use wisdom on who you tell when you find these gold deposits.

01:00:40.590 --> 01:00:46.798
It is almost like it is just laying out on the ground. God is going to provide supernaturally for you.

01:00:46.799 --> 01:01:08.339
It is going to raise up the churches; they are going to be places of provision for great revival, and it will spread throughout Africa. You say there has been such a drought and no provision.

01:01:08.340 --> 01:01:21.657
God is bringing provision, just like He did for the children of Israel in the wilderness when their clothes never tore or became tattered.

01:01:21.658 --> 01:01:32.286
There was an abundant supply of manna and quail each day. A rock even sprung forth water.

01:01:32.287 --> 01:02:01.806
God is going to bring water in the desert. It is not rain; it is coming right out of the ground, bubbling up.

01:02:01.807 --> 01:02:06.846
People will come for the water and they will get living water.

01:02:06.847 --> 01:02:20.756
Hallelujah. I don't know who I am talking to, but I rejoice with you.

01:02:20.758 --> 01:03:13.386
Gold in the least likely place, a place that is desolate and considered a wasteland.

01:03:13.387 --> 01:04:19.353
But it is not. Glory to God! Hallelujah! We call it so in the name of Jesus.

01:04:19.354 --> 01:04:30.903
Praise the Lord. We could go on with this for quite a while. We can pick up again tomorrow.

01:04:30.904 --> 01:04:45.737
Thank you, Father. Glory to God. Man, when I start singing like that, I am excited for you.

01:04:45.738 --> 01:04:50.146
I am excited for my brothers and sisters in Africa and for England.

01:04:50.147 --> 01:05:29.279
There is going to be a new wave, a new river. Get ready for a change in the tide.

